Notes on building a CAGEd_oPOSSUM database from input experiment, tag cluster,
tpm, tag count files.

General order of running scripts:
parse_experiments_file.pl
parse_tag_cluster_files.pl
parse_expression_files.pl
compute_tfbss.pl
update_is_tss_flag.pl


